<br>
being that the holidays just passed it was hard for me to respond to this post or the one before it by the poster.  for many reasons I believed this to be the same situation and the longer I withheld my feelings the more reasons for me to believe this is a similiar situation.<br>
<br>
this &quot;jen&quot; whom passed away just days before christmas passed away near where I live.  there has been no announcement of death in the paper and there was no funeral.  and also days after the tragedy her characters are bouncing around emarr gleefully being played by an aunt.<br>
<br>
in my opinion if i were to die and any of my friends/relatives were to log me on a few days later and have a ball with my characters i would hope that they would be told off.  and I dont see how the people playing could not assume that this could hurt someone who had been close to this person/player as a real life friend or just an in game associate.<br>
<br>
am I wrong for thinking this is just someone's cruel way of toying with our emotions just days before the holiday?  this put a lot of weight on me when I first found out that she was sick, then the sudden death, then the weird notifications that I received in private, and then her characters being played as if nothing bad happened at all...<br>
<br>
does anyone else have any ideas or feedback on this perticular situation?<br>
<br>
P.S.  I apologize for the anon post, I know this may seem heartless but it has had me confused, hurt, and full of mixed emotions and I couldnt bare to keep it inside, nor did I want to be resented for posting my thoughts and questions.  Im not trying to hurt anyone or bring up painful situations Im just looking for a bit of insight and maybe some closure to this situation that has me so intimatly involved.<br>
<br>
thank you,<br>
